(67441, 'Four Hundred Dawns (Galaxy 4, Part One)', 766, '<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i><br></p><p>The Doctor, Vicki and Steven arrive on an arid planet where they meet the beautiful Drahvins and the hideous Rills. Each has crash-landed after a confrontation in space. The Rills are friendly, compassionate explorers. The Drahvins are dull-witted, cloned soldiers, terrorised by the intelligent, warlike matriarch Maaga.</p><p>Both ships are damaged. The Drahvins'' craft is irreparable, but the Rills'' is almost ready to take off. Although unable to breathe the oxygen atmosphere, they employ efficient robot drones, which Vicki nicknames "Chumblies". Despite numerous offers by the Rills to take Maaga and her crew to safety, she refuses their aid. When the planet is discovered to be on the point of disintegration, Maaga tries to force the time travellers to help her steal the Rills'' ship and kill the Rills. Instead, the Doctor allows the Rills to draw power from the TARDIS to refuel and escape, leaving the Drahvins to their fate.</p>', 1, 3, '1965-09-11', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56268.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67441/doctor-who-3x01-four-hundred-dawns-galaxy-4-part-one'),
(67442, 'Trap of Steel (Galaxy 4, Part Two)', 766, '<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i></p><p>The Doctor, Vicki and Steven arrive on an arid planet where they meet the beautiful Drahvins and the hideous Rills. Each has crash-landed after a confrontation in space. The Rills are friendly, compassionate explorers. The Drahvins are dull-witted, cloned soldiers, terrorised by the intelligent, warlike matriarch Maaga.</p><p>Both ships are damaged. The Drahvins'' craft is irreparable, but the Rills'' is almost ready to take off. Although unable to breathe the oxygen atmosphere, they employ efficient robot drones, which Vicki nicknames "Chumblies". Despite numerous offers by the Rills to take Maaga and her crew to safety, she refuses their aid. When the planet is discovered to be on the point of disintegration, Maaga tries to force the time travellers to help her steal the Rills'' ship and kill the Rills. Instead, the Doctor allows the Rills to draw power from the TARDIS to refuel and escape, leaving the Drahvins to their fate.</p>', 2, 3, '1965-09-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56269.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67442/doctor-who-3x02-trap-of-steel-galaxy-4-part-two'),
(67443, 'Air Lock (Galaxy 4, Part Three)', 766, '<p>The Doctor, Vicki and Steven arrive on an arid planet where they meet the beautiful Drahvins and the hideous Rills. Each has crash-landed after a confrontation in space. The Rills are friendly, compassionate explorers. The Drahvins are dull-witted, cloned soldiers, terrorised by the intelligent, warlike matriarch Maaga.</p><p>Both ships are damaged. The Drahvins'' craft is irreparable, but the Rills'' is almost ready to take off. Although unable to breathe the oxygen atmosphere, they employ efficient robot drones, which Vicki nicknames "Chumblies". Despite numerous offers by the Rills to take Maaga and her crew to safety, she refuses their aid. When the planet is discovered to be on the point of disintegration, Maaga tries to force the time travellers to help her steal the Rills'' ship and kill the Rills. Instead, the Doctor allows the Rills to draw power from the TARDIS to refuel and escape, leaving the Drahvins to their fate.</p>', 3, 3, '1965-09-25', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56270.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67443/doctor-who-3x03-air-lock-galaxy-4-part-three'),
(67444, 'The Exploding Planet (Galaxy 4, Part Four)', 766, '<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i></p><p>The Doctor, Vicki and Steven arrive on an arid planet where they meet the beautiful Drahvins and the hideous Rills. Each has crash-landed after a confrontation in space. The Rills are friendly, compassionate explorers. The Drahvins are dull-witted, cloned soldiers, terrorised by the intelligent, warlike matriarch Maaga.</p><p>Both ships are damaged. The Drahvins'' craft is irreparable, but the Rills'' is almost ready to take off. Although unable to breathe the oxygen atmosphere, they employ efficient robot drones, which Vicki nicknames "Chumblies". Despite numerous offers by the Rills to take Maaga and her crew to safety, she refuses their aid. When the planet is discovered to be on the point of disintegration, Maaga tries to force the time travellers to help her steal the Rills'' ship and kill the Rills. Instead, the Doctor allows the Rills to draw power from the TARDIS to refuel and escape, leaving the Drahvins to their fate.</p>', 4, 3, '1965-10-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56271.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67444/doctor-who-3x04-the-exploding-planet-galaxy-4-part-four'),
(67445, 'Mission to the Unknown', 766, '<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i></p><p>On the planet Kembel, Space Security Service agent Marc Cory is investigating a recent sighting of a Dalek spaceship. His suspicion that the creatures may have established a base proves well-founded. He learns of a plot by the Daleks to invade and destroy the Solar System, but he is discovered and exterminated. The Daleks and their allies vow to conquer the universe, beginning with the planet Earth.</p>', 5, 3, '1965-10-09', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67445/doctor-who-3x05-mission-to-the-unknown'),
(67446, 'Temple of Secrets (The Myth Makers, Part One)', 766, '<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i></p><p>When the TARDIS arrives on the plains of Asia Minor not far from the besieged city of Troy, the Doctor is hailed by Achilles as the mighty godZeus and taken to the Greek camp. He meets Agamemnon and Odysseus. Forced to admit he is a mere mortal — albeit a traveller in space and time — he is given two days to devise a scheme to capture Troy.</p><p>Steven and Vicki, meanwhile, have been taken prisoner by the Trojans. Vicki, believed to possess supernatural powers, is given two days to banish the Greeks to prove she is not a spy.</p>', 6, 3, '1965-10-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56277.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67446/doctor-who-3x06-temple-of-secrets-the-myth-makers-part-one'),
