(323291, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part One', 766, '<p>In their search for the final segment of the ''Key To Time'', the Doctor and Romana land the TARDIS on the world of Atrios who is at war with it''s neighboring planet Zeos. Upon avoiding a missile attack right before landing, the Doctor and Time Lady Romana are then mistaken for spys from Zeos by the Marshall.</p>', 21, 16, '1979-01-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/146/367448.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323291/doctor-who-16x21-the-armageddon-factor-part-one'),
(323292, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Two', 766, '<p>When the Doctor and Romana work to escape they Marshal, they not only discover that their TARDIS has been buried underneath a pile of rubble from a recent Zeos attack, but also they discover someone who may be trapped and kidnapped by a unknown source.</p>', 22, 16, '1979-01-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/367674.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323292/doctor-who-16x22-the-armageddon-factor-part-two'),
(323293, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Three', 766, '<p>While faithful K-9 awaits the return of the Doctor and those with him, he is taken prisoner by The Shadow. With The Marshal determined to attack Zeos, the Doctor has to put a halt to his plan in order to save Atrios and billions of lives. </p>', 23, 16, '1979-02-03', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/367677.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323293/doctor-who-16x23-the-armageddon-factor-part-three'),
(323294, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Four', 766, '<p>K-9 communicates with the leader of the Zeos world and the Doctor attempts to keep the leader from completing it''s plan. The Doctor and companions discover the unknown world that is between Atrios and Zeos.</p>', 24, 16, '1979-02-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/367680.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323294/doctor-who-16x24-the-armageddon-factor-part-four'),
(323295, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Five', 766, '<p>The Doctor with Drax''s help, escape from their prison and work to stop The Shadows plan. The Shadow uses Astra to further the Black Guardians plot to obtain the Key to Time.</p>', 25, 16, '1979-02-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/367683.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323295/doctor-who-16x25-the-armageddon-factor-part-five'),
(323296, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Six', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Romana prevent the Marshal from concluding his plan and discover what the last segment of the Key to Time actually is. They then encounter both the Black Guardian and The White Guardian in their effort to conclude the mission given to them by the White Guardian.</p>', 26, 16, '1979-02-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/367684.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323296/doctor-who-16x26-the-armageddon-factor-part-six'),
(323299, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part One', 766, '<p>Romana experiments with regeneration while the Doctor prepares to land on a world that is experiencing periodic earthquakes and seems strangely familiar to him.</p>', 1, 17, '1979-09-01', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323299/doctor-who-17x01-destiny-of-the-daleks-part-one'),
(323300, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part Two', 766, '<p>After discovering that the world they are on is the Dalek''s home planet of Skaro, the Doctor starts to question the reason for the Movellans being there. Meanwhile, Romana is captured by the Daleks.</p>', 2, 17, '1979-09-08', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323300/doctor-who-17x02-destiny-of-the-daleks-part-two'),
