(323304, 'City of Death, Part One', 766, '<p>While the Doctor is exploring and showing the sights of Paris to Romana, they encounter what seems to be a blip in time. He then takes Romana to see the Mona Lisa and discovers a woman with Jewlery that seems out of place.</p>', 5, 17, '1979-09-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/158/396646.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323304/doctor-who-17x05-city-of-death-part-one'),
(323305, 'City of Death, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor, Romana and Duggan are taken prisoner by the Count and questioned about why the Doctor was so interested in the Countess''s bracelet.</p>', 6, 17, '1979-10-06', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323305/doctor-who-17x06-city-of-death-part-two'),
