(628774, 'Gloves Off', 618, '<p>Jimmy''s actions unexpectedly create waves for Kim. Meanwhile, Mike cautiously weighs a lucrative proposal that might bring about dire consequences.</p>', 4, 2, '2016-03-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/119756.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/628774/better-call-saul-2x04-gloves-off'),
(633518, 'Rebecca', 618, '<p>Jimmy becomes frustrated with his restrictive work environment. Meanwhile, Kim pulls out all the stops to dig herself out of a seemingly bottomless hole at HHM.</p>', 5, 2, '2016-03-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/48/122138.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/633518/better-call-saul-2x05-rebecca'),
(633789, 'Shoot', 101, '<p>In a defamation suit over a billboard he put up describing a gun store owner as a murderer. Also, a romantic rendezvous between Alicia and Jason is interrupted when Alicia learns that Grace is being accused of plagiarizing her college entrance essay.</p>', 17, 7, '2016-03-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/49/124444.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/633789/the-good-wife-7x17-shoot'),
(636926, 'Bali Ha''i', 618, '<p>Jimmy finds comfort in familiarity; Kim receives a life-changing proposal; when he is threatened, Mike finds himself pushed to the limit.</p>', 6, 2, '2016-03-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/49/124436.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636926/better-call-saul-2x06-bali-hai'),
(637936, 'Unmanned', 101, '<p>Alicia and Diane defend the privacy rights of a therapist whose neighbor, represented by attorney Caitlyn D''Arcy, flies a drone over his home office. Also, Assistant U.S. Attorney Connor Fox attempts to use Eli''s daughter, Marissa, as leverage in the case against Peter, and the power struggle at Lockhart, Agos &amp; Lee reaches a boiling point.</p>', 18, 7, '2016-03-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/50/127179.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/637936/the-good-wife-7x18-unmanned'),
(645687, 'Inflatable', 618, '<p>Mike''s growing frustration shows when his hand is forced, but with Jimmy''s help, he works to keep the peace. Meanwhile, Jimmy boldly forges a new path forward.</p>', 7, 2, '2016-03-28', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/50/127351.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645687/better-call-saul-2x07-inflatable'),
(645688, 'Fifi', 618, '<p>Mike is determined to settle the score with a dangerous adversary. An unexpected opportunity to gain a competitive edge falls in Jimmy''s lap.</p>', 8, 2, '2016-04-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/51/129601.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645688/better-call-saul-2x08-fifi'),
(645689, 'Nailed', 618, '<p>Mike takes a methodical approach to his mission. Someone questions Chuck''s capabilities. Jimmy faces a personal dilemma.</p>', 9, 2, '2016-04-11', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/131855.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645689/better-call-saul-2x09-nailed'),
(645691, 'Klick', 618, '<p>Jimmy is forced to make a hard choice. Mike takes matters into his own hands. Hamlin relays shocking news while Chuck''s condition continues to evolve.</p>', 10, 2, '2016-04-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/53/134070.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645691/better-call-saul-2x10-klick'),
(660557, 'Tick Tock, Bitches', 177, '<p>After Hanna''s shocking abduction by "Uber A," the PLLs and company desperately race against the clock to save one of their own. The only way to do this is by handing over evidence of Charlotte''s real murderer to "Uber A." In order to do so, the girls must decide what blatant lines they are willing to cross that they have never breached before; and once they cross that line, there is no turning back.</p>', 1, 7, '2016-06-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/63/159448.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/660557/pretty-little-liars-7x01-tick-tock-bitches'),
(663426, 'Landing', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca travel to Toronto to represent NSA Agent Jeff Delinger who was detained by customs officers while attempting to re-enter the United States. Also, Diane grows concerned when her husband, Kurt McVeigh, decides to retire and sell his business to Holly Westfall, a rival business owner, and Peter contemplates an uncertain future when he faces possible arrest.</p>', 19, 7, '2016-04-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/53/134251.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663426/the-good-wife-7x19-landing'),
(663427, 'Party', 101, '<p>Alicia''s night goes from bad to worse when she throws a party to celebrate Howard and Jackie''s upcoming wedding. Also, Eli asks Jason to investigate Peter in preparation for his trial.</p>', 20, 7, '2016-04-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/54/136968.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663427/the-good-wife-7x20-party'),
(663428, 'Verdict', 101, '<p>As Peter''s trial begins, Alicia works desperately to keep her husband from returning to jail. Also, Diane and Lucca move aggressively to expand the law firm, but face serious opposition from David Lee.</p>', 21, 7, '2016-05-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/55/138927.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663428/the-good-wife-7x21-verdict'),
(664672, 'Home', 82, '<p>Bran trains with the Three-Eyed Raven. In King''s Landing, Jaime advises Tommen. Tyrion demands good news, but has to make his own. At Castle Black, the Night''s Watch stands behind Thorne. Ramsay Bolton proposes a plan, and Balon Greyjoy entertains other proposals.</p>', 2, 6, '2016-05-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142372.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664672/game-of-thrones-6x02-home'),
(664673, 'Oathbreaker', 82, '<p>Daenerys meets her future. Bran meets the past. Tommen confronts the High Sparrow. Arya trains to be No One. Varys finds an answer. Ramsay gets a gift.</p>', 3, 6, '2016-05-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142370.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664673/game-of-thrones-6x03-oathbreaker'),
(664674, 'Book of the Stranger', 82, '<p>Tyrion strikes a deal. Jorah and Daario undertake a difficult task. Jaime and Cersei try to improve their situation.</p>', 4, 6, '2016-05-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664674/game-of-thrones-6x04-book-of-the-stranger'),
(664675, 'The Door', 82, '<p>Tyrion seeks a strange ally. Bran learns a great deal. Brienne goes on a mission. Arya is given a chance to prove herself.</p>', 5, 6, '2016-05-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/60/150273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664675/game-of-thrones-6x05-the-door'),
(664676, 'Blood of My Blood', 82, '<p>An old foe comes back into the picture. Gilly meets Sam''s family. Arya faces a difficult choice. Jaime faces off against the High Sparrow.</p>', 6, 6, '2016-05-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/60/150274.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664676/game-of-thrones-6x06-blood-of-my-blood'),
(698499, 'Bedlam', 177, '<p>With the fallout of Hanna''s abduction still weighing heavily on the PLLs, the Liars begin to grow suspicious of Elliott Rollins as Ali''s condition worsens. Tensions rise between Liam, Aria and Ezra as they work on the book together. Spencer and Caleb are on edge, as neither of them want to talk about the awkward elephant in the room. Meanwhile, Emily receives a disturbing phone call and tries to find a way to see Ali.</p>', 2, 7, '2016-06-28', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/64/162323.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/698499/pretty-little-liars-7x02-bedlam'),
(717449, 'The Broken Man', 82, '<p>The High Sparrow eyes another target. Jaime confronts a hero. Arya makes a plan. The North is reminded.</p>', 7, 6, '2016-06-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/60/150275.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/717449/game-of-thrones-6x07-the-broken-man'),
(729573, 'No One', 82, '<p>Jaime encounters a hero; the High Sparrow fixates on another prey; Arya hatches a new plan; Yara and Theon plot their next move; Olenna and Cersei discuss their families'' futures.</p><p></p><p>While Jaime weighs his options, Cersei answers a request. Tyrion''s plans bear fruit. Arya faces a new test.</p>', 8, 6, '2016-06-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/61/153044.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/729573/game-of-thrones-6x08-no-one'),
(729574, 'Battle of the Bastards', 82, '<p>Ramsay surprises his audience. Jon retaliates. Dany is true to her word.</p>', 9, 6, '2016-06-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/62/155042.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/729574/game-of-thrones-6x09-battle-of-the-bastards'),
(729575, 'The Winds of Winter', 82, '<p>Alliances are made, the High Sparrow is holding trials at King''s Landing, Daenerys is sailing for the Seven Kingdoms and a new King of the North is crowned.</p>', 10, 6, '2016-06-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/63/157920.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/729575/game-of-thrones-6x10-the-winds-of-winter'),
