(1098151, 'Social Media and Its Discontents', 18206, '<p>After landing tech mogul Neil Gross as a new client, the firm is tasked with figuring out a way to combat hate speech on his social media platform. Maia''s suspicions about her father grow after Uncle Jax pays an unwelcome visit. Lucca and Colin''s romance heats up.</p>', 6, 1, '2017-03-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/102/256992.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1098151/the-good-fight-1x06-social-media-and-its-discontents'),
(1102456, 'Not So Grand Jury', 18206, '<p>Mike Kresteva takes his case against Reddick, Boseman &amp; Kolstad to a grand jury, but the firm devises a grand jury strategy of their own to hamper Kresteva''s efforts. Colin finds himself in an awkward position in court.</p>', 7, 1, '2017-03-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/103/259755.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1102456/the-good-fight-1x07-not-so-grand-jury'),
(1104767, 'The Law of Non-Contradiction', 32, '<p>Gloria revisits her stepfather''s past to try and find some answers.</p>', 3, 3, '2017-05-03', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/110/275788.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104767/fargo-3x03-the-law-of-non-contradiction'),
(1104768, 'The Narrow Escape Problem', 32, '<p>Emmit and Sy try to figure out what they''ve gotten themselves into, Nikki and Ray track down some collateral, and Gloria learns more about Maurice.</p>', 4, 3, '2017-05-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/111/278144.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104768/fargo-3x04-the-narrow-escape-problem'),
(1104769, 'The House of Special Purpose', 32, '<p>Nikki and Ray''s retaliation has consequences for Emmit. Meanwhile, Gloria and Winnie start connecting the dots.</p>', 5, 3, '2017-05-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/280989.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104769/fargo-3x05-the-house-of-special-purpose'),
(1104770, 'The Lord of No Mercy', 32, '<p>Gloria and Winnie get closer to the truth, Emmit tries to make things right, Nikki and Ray prepare for payback and Varga cleans up a mess.</p>', 6, 3, '2017-05-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/113/283603.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104770/fargo-3x06-the-lord-of-no-mercy'),
(1104771, 'The Law of Inevitability', 32, '<p>Gloria tries to work around the system, Nikki finds herself in a familiar place, Varga comes up with an alternative plan and Emmit goes to dinner.</p>', 7, 3, '2017-05-31', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286958.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104771/fargo-3x07-the-law-of-inevitability'),
(1104772, 'Who Rules the Land of Denial?', 32, '<p>Nikki struggles to survive, Emmit gets spooked and Sy joins Varga for tea.</p>', 8, 3, '2017-06-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/115/289499.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104772/fargo-3x08-who-rules-the-land-of-denial'),
(1104773, 'Aporia', 32, '<p>Emmit sits down with Gloria, while Nikki negotiates a deal.</p>', 9, 3, '2017-06-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/291842.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104773/fargo-3x09-aporia'),
(1104774, 'Somebody to Love', 32, '<p>Gloria follows the money, Nikki plays a game and Emmit learns a lesson about progress from Varga.</p>', 10, 3, '2017-06-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/117/294266.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1104774/fargo-3x10-somebody-to-love'),
(1112271, 'Reddick v Boseman', 18206, '<p>Founding partner, Carl Reddick, makes a surprise return to the firm. A renowned local pastor needs the firm''s help in a legal matter that threatens to ruin his legacy. Lucca unexpectedly meets Colin''s parents. Meanwhile, Henry attempts to reconnect with Maia.</p>', 8, 1, '2017-04-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/105/262868.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1112271/the-good-fight-1x08-reddick-v-boseman'),
(1119144, 'The Rickshank Rickdemption', 216, '<p>Rick, still in galactic prison, puts an intricate escape plan into action. Back on Earth, which is now under federation control, Morty and Summer have an argument about their grandpa.</p>', 1, 3, '2017-04-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/105/262759.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1119144/rick-and-morty-3x01-the-rickshank-rickdemption'),
(1119338, 'Self Condemned', 18206, '<p>Diane and Adrian find themselves involved in another police brutality case, this time representing a surprising but familiar face, Colin Sweeney. Lucca represents Maia for her interview with a federal investigator seeking information on the Rindell scandal.</p>', 9, 1, '2017-04-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/106/265861.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1119338/the-good-fight-1x09-self-condemned'),
(1127054, 'Chaos', 18206, '<p>Diane takes on a new client who is accused of cyber-terrorism, resulting in unforeseen repercussions for the firm, especially Lucca. An accident brings Diane and Kurt together. Henry reveals new truths about the scandal to Maia.</p>', 10, 1, '2017-04-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268622.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1127054/the-good-fight-1x10-chaos'),
(1144079, 'Rickmancing the Stone', 216, '<p>With the kids dealing with their parents'' divorce, Rick takes them to a Mad Max-style universe where he tries to steal a green crystal from a group of scavengers.</p>', 2, 3, '2017-07-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/122/306764.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1144079/rick-and-morty-3x02-rickmancing-the-stone'),
(1150962, 'Efectuar lo acordado', 27436, '<p>The professor recruits Tokio and 7 other criminals for a grand heist, targeting the Royal Mint of Spain.</p>', 1, 1, '2017-05-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/353374.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1150962/la-casa-de-papel-1x01-efectuar-lo-acordado'),
(1150963, 'Imprudencias letales', 27436, '<p>Hostage negotiator Raquel makes initial contact with the Professor. One of the hostages is a crucial part of the thieves'' plans.</p>', 2, 1, '2017-05-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/353375.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1150963/la-casa-de-papel-1x02-imprudencias-letales'),
(1150964, 'Errar al disparar', 27436, '<p>A new step of the robbers will lead the police to act more quickly. Inspector Murillo will not hesitate to give the green light against the Dalís who will go outside of the FNMT. How many lives will the biggest heist in history take?</p>', 3, 1, '2017-05-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/353800.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1150964/la-casa-de-papel-1x03-errar-al-disparar'),
(1150965, 'Caballo de Troya', 27436, '<p>Sub-Inspector Ángel will be one of the policemen who will set foot inside the National Currency and Stamp Factory, but also, Suarez, the head of the GEOs, will try to camouflage himself among the other hostages. Will they succeed?</p>', 4, 1, '2017-05-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/354285.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1150965/la-casa-de-papel-1x04-caballo-de-troya'),
(1150966, 'El día de la marmota', 27436, '<p>The biggest robbery in history also has loose ends and The Professor never thought he was in such a difficult situation. Raquel will travel to the origin of the plan and find an important clue. Will they discover The Professor?</p>', 5, 1, '2017-05-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/354284.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1150966/la-casa-de-papel-1x05-el-dia-de-la-marmota'),
(1156192, 'Slip', 618, '<p>Jimmy is pushed to desperate measures; Nacho picks up a skill; Mike explores an alliance; Kim stands up to Hamlin.</p>', 8, 3, '2017-06-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/115/288801.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1156192/better-call-saul-3x08-slip'),
(1156193, 'Fall', 618, '<p>Jimmy visits a friend and takes up an old pastime; Chuck and Hamlin argue over the future of the firm; Kim faces challenges.</p>', 9, 3, '2017-06-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/291427.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1156193/better-call-saul-3x09-fall'),
(1156194, 'Lantern', 618, '<p>Kim takes time off; Jimmy tries to make amends; Nacho gambles with his future; Hamlin pushes Chuck to make a decision.</p>', 10, 3, '2017-06-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/117/293899.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1156194/better-call-saul-3x10-lantern'),
